name: Vision Programming Project
body:
### Welcome to Vision Programming Project
Here you can see our first project on Github. We are 2 main distributors and 1 new greenhorn. 
Our project is based on trinitycore, with several fixes. 

***
How to compile the Core?
http://www.trinitycore.info 

You can use the Core and the Custom things for your Server. If you like to use the Custom things pls send me a request if you could do this.
